snippet.title: There’s More to Explore at Camp Pokémon! (360 Video)
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/2eQPGeJ
Spend your summer at Camp Pokémon! With a fun new activity to enjoy, and Alola region Pokémon to discover, it’s a great way to introduce a young Trainer to the world of Pokémon. Visit our site to learn more about the exciting new update to the Camp Pokémon app!

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon 
Twitter: http://twitter.com/Pokemon 
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon 
Tumblr: http://www.pokemon.tumblr.com
